Just as the illusion exists in love,

72
00:09:06,985 --> 00:09:10,045
the illusion you can never forget,

73
00:09:10,122 --> 00:09:14,616
so I was under the illusion
I would never forget hiroshima.

74
00:09:14,926 --> 00:09:17,554
Just like with love.

75
00:09:25,036 --> 00:09:27,698
I saw the survivors too,

76
00:09:27,773 --> 00:09:31,231
and those who were in the wombs
of the women of hiroshima.

77
00:09:32,043 --> 00:09:34,341
I saw the patience,

78
00:09:34,546 --> 00:09:36,173
the innocence,

79
00:09:36,648 --> 00:09:39,617
the apparent meekness

80
00:09:39,684 --> 00:09:42,778
with which the temporary survivors
of hiroshima

81
00:09:42,854 --> 00:09:45,914
adapted to a fate so unjust

82
00:09:45,991 --> 00:09:49,290
that the imagination,
usually so fertile,

83
00:09:49,394 --> 00:09:52,886
is silent before it.

84
