97
00:10:46,952 --> 00:10:49,716
Entire cities rise up in anger.

98
00:10:50,755 --> 00:10:54,213
But against whom
do they rise up in anger?

99
00:10:54,659 --> 00:10:57,753
The anger of entire cities,
whether they like it or not,

100
00:10:57,863 --> 00:10:59,990
against the principle
of inequality advanced

101
00:11:00,098 --> 00:11:03,363
by one people against another.

102
