The seven branches of the delta estuary

134
00:13:18,603 --> 00:13:20,503
of the river ota

135
00:13:20,605 --> 00:13:25,008
drain and fill at their usual hour,

136
00:13:25,443 --> 00:13:29,311
precisely at their usual hour,

137
00:13:29,414 --> 00:13:33,214
with fresh water rich with fish,
grey or blue,

138
00:13:33,318 --> 00:13:35,411
depending on the season
and time of day.

139
00:13:36,621 --> 00:13:40,113
People along the muddy banks
no longer watch

140
